      "writtenOn": "2020-04-09T21:15:44Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The base class does handle the semaphore part of GrFlushInfo so I\u0027m definitely all for sharing code if we can here. My only worry is that each backend does have a unique way of handling finish procs and knowing when they are done, so I think it would be hard to find a common API that they all use. Though I do like that general idea so I\u0027ll think about some, but I think its a better change for a follow on CL if we can think of a good API that everything can use.",
